KDC\
  Runs as a single process and provides 2 services\
	Authentication Server				-			provides the TGT\
	Ticket Granting Server				-			application server that issues service tickets\
  and a database\
	Kerberos database (aka Admin Server)	-			the database has the record of each principal. It is a centralized repository of kerberos and contains the identification of clients and their access\
\
