Kerberos Ticket \
Think of this as a certificate issued by an authentication server, encrypted using the server key\
issues to a client\
2 types of tickets\
	TGT\
	Service Ticket\
\
\
Ticket Granting Ticket (authentication ticket)\
   the following are encrypted by the TGS secret key\
	client ID\
	client network address\
	timestamp\
	lifetime\
\
\
Service Ticket\
	Principal 		-		could be a user, host or service\
	session key	-		encrypted by the KDC server key, used for authentication of the principal to the verifier\
	timestamp		-		\
